ActOther Than Statutory Authority
SubjectCanada-Kingdom of Bahrain - Exchange of information on tax matters ** Agreement **
PrecisOrder authorizing the Minister of Foreign Affairs to take the actions necessary, on behalf of Canada, to BRING INTO FORCE the AGREEMENT between the Government of CANADA and the Government of the KINGDOM OF BAHRAIN for the EXCHANGE OF INFORMATION ON TAX MATTERS.
